latestPosts.caption:
At The Met Gala, every detail tells a story, and for #Ciara the look started at the roots. From concept to carpet, I needed something that could keep up with the vision. The @lorealpro AirLight Pro dryer gave me the power, shine, and precision to bring it to life.

We went with a sculpted, high-shine bixie—sleek at the crown, contoured to the head, and full of life. A modern, edgy silhouette that felt tough yet feminine all at once.

Drop a 🖤 if you’re loving this Met Gala moment!

#AirlightProPartner #AirLightProAmbassador #MetGala2025 #MetGalaHair #TheMet #MetGlam #Ciara
